<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.4">
<l>paimpoḻil vāḻkuyil kāḷmayil kāḷoṇ karuviḷaikāḷ</l>
<l>vampak kaḷaṅkaṉi kāḷvaṇṇap pūvai naṟumalarkāḷ</l>
<l>aimperum pātakar kāḷaṇi māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>emperu māṉuṭai yaniṟa muṅkaḷuk keṉceyvatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O koels that live in the green groves! O peacocks!</l>
<l>O bright mussel-shell creeper flowers! O fresh kaḷā-berries!</l>
<l>O pretty, fragrant bilberry flowers! O five great sinners!</l>
<l>What [will] you do with the hue of the Lord from the beautiful Māliruñcōlai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
